org.opengis.cite.iso19142

Class FeatureTypeInfo

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.opengis.cite.iso19142.FeatureTypeInfo

  • public class FeatureTypeInfo
extends Object
    Provides information about a feature type managed by a WFS. Much of the information is gleaned from the service description (wfs:WFS_Capabilities).

        public void setDefaultCRS(String crsRef)
